duet is a 1994 tamil musical film directed by k. balachander . the film features prabhu and meenakshi sheshadri in the lead roles , with meenakshi seshadri , ramesh aravind and meenakshi seshadri in the lead roles . the film 's score and soundtrack are composed by a. r. rahman . the film was a remake of tamil film &lt;unk&gt; .